#****f* lyricue/save_song_as
# NAME
#   save_song_as
# SYNOPSIS
#   save_song_as ()
# FUNCTION
#   Save the song as new name, close the add window
#   and update the available songs
# INPUTS
# OUTPUT
#   Calls a few others to do anything
# SOURCE
