#****f* lyricue/create_search
# NAME
#   create_search
# SYNOPSIS
#   create_search ($topwidgets)
# FUNCTION
#   Create the dialog for advanced search
# INPUTS
#   $topwidgets - Widgets of main window
# OUTPUT
#   Search dialog
# SOURCE
